@startuml Saldytuvas Plus - Deployment Diagrama (Web Application)
!theme plain
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam defaultTextAlignment center
skinparam linetype ortho

title Saldytuvas Plus - Deployment Diagrama (Web Application - Production)

' ============================================
' CLIENT DEVICES (Vartotojo įrenginiai)
' ============================================

node "Client Device" <<device>> as ClientDevice {
  artifact "browser" as Browser
}

' ============================================
' CLOUD INFRASTRUCTURE
' ============================================

node "Supabase Cloud" <<executionEnvironment>> as SupabaseCloud {
  component instance "Supabase Database" <<database>> as SupabaseDB {
    database "PostgreSQL" as PostgreSQL
  }
  
  component instance "Supabase Auth" <<service>> as SupabaseAuth
  component instance "Supabase Storage" <<storage>> as SupabaseStorage
  component instance "Supabase Edge Functions" <<server>> as SupabaseEdge
  
  artifact "database.ddl" as DatabaseDdl
  artifact "migrations/*.sql" as Migrations
}

node "Web Hosting" <<executionEnvironment>> as WebHosting {
  component instance "Flutter Web App" <<application>> as FlutterWebApp {
    artifact "clientPages/*.dart" as ClientPagesArtifact
    artifact "clientControllers/*.dart" as ClientControllersArtifact
    artifact "models/*.dart" as ModelsArtifact
    artifact "services/*.dart" as ServicesArtifact
    artifact "repositories/*.dart" as RepositoriesArtifact
  }
}

node "External APIs" <<executionEnvironment>> as ExternalAPIs {
  component instance "Gemini API" <<server>> as GeminiAPI
  component instance "Spoonacular API" <<server>> as SpoonacularAPI
  component instance "OpenFoodFacts API" <<server>> as OpenFoodFactsAPI
}

' ============================================
' RYŠIAI: Client → Web Hosting
' ============================================

ClientDevice ..> WebHosting : HTTPS\n<<use>>

' ============================================
' RYŠIAI: Web Hosting → Supabase Cloud
' ============================================

FlutterWebApp ..> SupabaseDB : HTTPS\n<<use>>
FlutterWebApp ..> SupabaseAuth : HTTPS\n<<use>>
FlutterWebApp ..> SupabaseStorage : HTTPS\n<<use>>

' ============================================
' RYŠIAI: Web Hosting → External APIs
' ============================================

FlutterWebApp ..> GeminiAPI : HTTPS\n<<use>>
FlutterWebApp ..> SpoonacularAPI : HTTPS\n<<use>>
FlutterWebApp ..> OpenFoodFactsAPI : HTTPS\n<<use>>

' ============================================
' RYŠIAI: Supabase vidiniai
' ============================================

SupabaseDB ..> PostgreSQL : uses
PostgreSQL ..> DatabaseDdl <<manifest>>
PostgreSQL ..> Migrations <<manifest>>

SupabaseEdge ..> SupabaseDB : uses

' ============================================
' LEGEND
' ============================================
legend right
  **Deployment Node'ų tipai:**
  - <<device>> : Vartotojo įrenginys
  - <<executionEnvironment>> : Execution Environment (Cloud/Server)
  - <<database>> : Duomenų bazė
  - <<server>> : Serveris/Paslauga
  - <<storage>> : Saugykla
  - <<application>> : Aplikacija
  
  **Ryšiai:**
  ..> : komunikacija (HTTPS)
  <<manifest>> : manifestuoja (fizinis failas)
  <<use>> : naudoja
endlegend

note right of ClientDevice
  **Web Client:**
  - Browser (Chrome, Firefox, Safari, Edge)
  - Veikia visose platformose
  - Nereikia instaliacijos
  - Artifact: browser
end note

note right of WebHosting
  **Web Hosting (Flutter Web):**
  - Firebase Hosting / Vercel / Netlify
  - Flutter build: `flutter build web`
  - Compiled Dart → JavaScript
  - Artifacts: clientPages/*.dart, 
    clientControllers/*.dart,
    models/*.dart, services/*.dart,
    repositories/*.dart
end note

note right of SupabaseCloud
  **Supabase Cloud Infrastructure:**
  - Managed PostgreSQL database (production)
  - Authentication service (production)
  - File storage (receipts, images)
  - Edge Functions (serverless)
  - HTTPS endpoint: https://xxx.supabase.co
end note

@enduml

















